The National Executive Council Committee of the Academic Staff Union of Universities (ASUU) says there is no document to prove that the Minister of Communications and Digital Economy, Isa Pantami is a cyber security expert. The union also faulted the promotion of the Minister to professor of cyber security by the Federal University of Technology, Owerri, Imo State. Isa Pantami In September 2021, the Governor of Zamfara State, Bello Matawalle, placed commercials in newspapers congratulating Pantami on his promotion to a Professor of Cybersecurity. Pantami was among seven Readers (Associate Professors) promoted to Professor by the Governing Council of Federal University of Technology Owerri (FUTO) at its 186th meeting held on August 20, 2021. Since then, FUTO and Pantami have both been at the end of public criticism over the circumstances surrounding the minister’s promotion to the highest academic rank in the institution. 



