10 Hours Ago





Also, last Monday, ASUU declared the promotion as illegal at a press conference addressed by the President of ASUU, Prof. Emmanuel Osodeke. Meanwhile, a probe panel set up by the FUTO Chapter of ASUU had claimed the university followed due process in the appointment of the minister as Professor of Cyber Security. However, a report from the NEC Committee, which was obtained by SaharaReporters on Monday, exposed the lack of documents to show that Pantami was an expert in cyber security. 



